  "altLabel": "SoftWare Hash Identifier",
  "notation": "SWHID",
  "definition": "SWHIDs are persistent, intrinsic identifiers for software source code artifacts such as source code files, source trees, commits, and other objects typically found in version control systems.",
  "scopeNote": "A SWHID includes a mandatory core identifier and optional qualifiers to express context and subparts.",
